  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They robbed the cellar of the factory of a-- a shipment of coconut butter, which we used for cosmetics.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But everything was all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were sort of thinking what to do, and how to arrange, and how to expend the-- expend the dollar, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The people making sausages and black market buying butter, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All sorts of food, and a few-- a week or so later, the people who ran away on the 7th of September started coming back.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some-- they were coming back, and most-- the one we knew-- coming back to pick up families.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were telling stories about Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're so good, and they're so nice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you see, not like Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Robin was playing-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] poker with a friend who had a wholesale bakery supplies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And another boy was in the same sort of poker school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had the idea that we'd better go because, also, an uncle of my wife came back to pick up his family who-- which he never did.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he had the intention-- and telling the stories that because we can sell watches, we can make money, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a lot of people, there was an industry of smuggling stuff from there to there because the Germans wanted watches.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- and you can buy cheap Polish zlotys over there, which were still good in the-- in thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he said, and we took up, you see, that these two boys, you see, [? they're ?] from this poker school with the wife-- my wife, and myself, and a few friends when he said that he can take 12 people and bring all the stuff, what you can sell.",
      "word_count": 51
    }
  ],
